### Actuator health
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### List sensitive words
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sensitive-words?page=0&size=20

### Sanitize text
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sanitize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "inputText": "This message contains testbadword and a restricted phrase.",
  "sourceSystem": "http-file"
}

### Create sensitive word
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sensitive-words
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "word": "local-demo-term",
  "severityLevel": 2,
  "active": true
}

### Patch sensitive word
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/sensitive-words/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "severityLevel": 3
}
